I"(<p>Phantom Chess is an <strong>auto-chess</strong> game built for <a href="https://itch.io/jam/geta-game-jam-8">Geta Game Jam 8</a>. The player plays against the AI and tries to reach the highest level they can. The game goes on till the player loses. It functions as a regular auto-chess game where the player can buy/sell units, upgrade them via combining 3, etc.</p>

<p>The game was built using the <strong>Unity3D</strong> engine and written in <strong>C#</strong>. I worked in a team of two on this, as a <strong>gameplay programmer</strong>. I programmed the combat, movement and combination functionalities that were core to the game, among other features.</p>

